{"tid":561464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"年廿九適逢情人節　年宵檔旺場","createTime":"2018-02-15T04:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T08:59:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bb76529c54bfeb7628133c78a2fd45256f847201","tid":561464,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T04:31:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180215/20306183\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180215%2F20306183&d=X8FF1IDY7L640IgtqOALIzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=02798615\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180215%2F20306183&h=c97a33f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180215/20306183</a><br />\n<br />\n年廿九適逢情人節　年宵檔旺場<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180215/large/15la7p08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180215%2Flarge%2F15la7p08.jpg&h=7b5df704&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨年廿九適逢情人節，維園年宵人潮不斷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今日是年宵最後一日，昨年廿九適逢情人節，維園年宵人潮擁擠得水洩不通，年花和乾貨檔的生意長做長有，多名檔主表明不會減價。不過有賣巴士模型的攤檔則減價20%，「好想盡快賣晒啲貨。」<br />\n<br />\n教育大學一群學生以霓虹燈作主題，人手紮作「香港」、「心想事成」、等詞的霓虹燈飾，在年宵出售，各售280元和380元不等，非常熱賣，謝同學和梁同學笑指，昨日已經回本，「終於可以賺利是錢」，亦有不少情侶購買「我愛你」字樣的燈飾，昨日賣剩數個。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180215/large/a0804a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180215%2Flarge%2Fa0804a.gif&h=89a78552&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴士模型銷情慘淡<br />\n<br />\n有以狗年作主題的乾貨檔主以狗公仔髮夾作招徠，以20元一個低價出售，亦已賣出60%存貨。負責人翁先生指，不少男士昨購買髮夾送給女朋友，相信最後一日生意理想，不打算減價。鄭先生和朋友在年宵開檔賣狗公仔、文件套，並一併替友人寄售巴士模型。早前大埔發生九巴車禍，他說不知道模型銷情慘淡是否與慘劇有關，但已將售價由500多元減價至300多元，不排除會繼續減價。<br />\n<br />\n■記者廖梓霖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t花車照巡遊旅發局︰國際隊伍難取消行程<br />\n港聞 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t團年飯加價　龍蝦$2,388一隻<br />\n港聞 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t瑪麗義工團　狗仔冷帽迎新春B<br />\n港聞 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t煙花取消變齋睇維港　船團拒全數退款<br />\n港聞 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t深水埗明火墟市今開爐單親媽湊女賣熟食「想賺番滿足感」<br />\n港聞 5小時前"},{"pid":"f978a4d2c2f048c48ce7528bd0b1ded61fe07fbc","tid":561464,"uid":48582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T07:40:27.000Z","msg":"巴士反車同巴士模型有乜撚嘢關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14bafc4d48e9a42a32f1c71ddf064e4bc6e6a707","tid":561464,"uid":55851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180215/large/a0804a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180215%2Flarge%2Fa0804a.gif&h=c5cd2b01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢堆野全部取消晒佢唔該，做人比返少少良心同人性，香港發生咁大悲劇應該低調留返喺屋企"},{"pid":"b54c01fef7e5ec5a3336f469570c99e5996280b7","tid":561464,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T08:59:57.000Z","msg":"哪有女"}]}